item.description:
Join local holistic and mental health professionals from the Greater Boston Area by attending a networking event to meet each other! Bring friends and colleagues.

Whether you are a future practitioner or seasoned therapist with an established practice, you will greatly benefit from networking with local therapists and holistic practitioners! Join with professionals from several established local Networking Associations as we collaborate and connect to strengthen our practices and communities!

Location:

Finale
1306 Beacon St
Brookline, MA


Hosted by
Betty Chan, Organizer of the Greater Boston Mental Health Professionals Meetup Group
Linda Marks, Organizer of the Boston Area Mind-Body Therapies Meetup Group

Cost : $20.00
**** Must be paid IN ADVANCE by sending payment to ....
Linda Marks
3 Central Ave
Newton, MA 02460

Includes admission to the event, facilitated networking and introductions, cash bar, raffle opportunities, and, “To Put The Icing On The Cake,” a great feast of Finale’s BEST desserts!

To RSVP or for questions, Contact Linda Marks 617-965-7846 LSMHEART@aol.com
item.name: How SWEET It Is! Holistic & Mental Health Networking Event at Finale
